body:
@pwmcintyre with some more testing, I realized the work is not complete to make it work smoothly.

You might have it running under some specific conditions, and I am glad this could unblock you, but this is still failing in the general case.

The reason is that `flatten`  by default uses the `SkipSchemas`  flattening option, which atm does not rebase the underlying `$ref`s in schemas. Still some more work on that...

@fredbi -- no problem

I've been wondering how you'll go about merging this in considering how it does change the way $refs work, it may be incompatible with other peoples setup ... so i totally understand

let me know if there's anything you need from me
